## Asset Compilation

```yaml
# config/deploy.yml

# Assets are compiled during build
# Using Thruster for asset serving

asset_path: /rails/public/assets

# Kamal automatically:
# 1. Runs rails assets:precompile
# 2. Includes assets in Docker image
# 3. Serves via Thruster
```

